        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 72–73. Cybaeus ubicki spec. nov., male from Novato, California, left palpus. 72 Patellar apophysis, ventral. 73 Proximal arm of tegular apophysis, ventral. Arrows indicate diagnostic characters (72 dorsal prominence of patellar apophysis, 73 ventral longitudinal groove of proximal arm of tegular apophysis)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4752611/files/figure.png" .

